N(t0) thn t0 

N(t0) /N0 = exp(-t/T)        ----->     pithanothta    diaspashs 

1 - exp(-t/T)                ----->     pithanothta mh diaspashs


an o tyxaios arithmos einai < 1- exp(-t/T) tote exw diaspash 

mesos xronos zwhs einai  o xronos ston opoio exw meiwsh pyrhnwn kata paragontai apo 1/e 
